{"tid":2441360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警國安處長突還清按揭","createTime":"2021-03-10T15:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T15:42:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52733fd0f2ac45e07e2bda2150a1341ccd2d9894","tid":2441360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/ZAVYPYEVVVAR7AQXCCSTGRAZOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FZAVYPYEVVVAR7AQXCCSTGRAZOU%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=7e0a747d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FZAVYPYEVVVAR7AQXCCSTGRAZOU%2F&h=93736fc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/ZAVYPYEVVVAR7AQXCCSTGRAZOU/</a><br />\n<br />\n警國安處長突還清按揭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2deb9Qxj4E4jwXiUAKNFnP_j-H4=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/454P6IAZPJG47HCHCHBZDOECWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2deb9Qxj4E4jwXiUAKNFnP_j-H4%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F454P6IAZPJG47HCHCHBZDOECWI.jpg&h=f1aa34df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國安處長蔡展鵬<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國財政部今年1月因應香港警方國安處大搜捕民主派人士，宣佈制裁六名執行港版國安法的官員，包括警務處國安處處長蔡展鵬及助理處長江學禮。資料顯示，繼江學禮上月底一筆過還清銀行貸款後，蔡展鵬上周二亦向恒生銀行還清火炭御龍山單位按揭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人行黨委同日稱美制裁無效<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行黨委書記、銀保監會主席郭樹清上周二向傳媒聲稱，在香港的金融機構，不論中資或外資，都不會按美國的要求執行制裁，聲言美國的制裁毫無約束力。<br />\n<br />\n不過，資料顯示，郭樹清發表上述言論同日，被美國制裁的蔡展鵬就還清其物業按揭貸款。蔡展鵬2014年以837萬元買入御龍山六座一個中層單位，當時先在滙豐銀行承造按揭，2017年轉按至恒生銀行，兩筆按揭均註冊「All moneys」，未能得知按揭金額。惟根據最新資料，蔡展鵬上周二已還清按揭貸款。<br />\n<br />\n有關單位建築面積991平方呎，實用面積775平方呎，根據銀行最新估價，單位現時市值約1,309萬元，賬面升值472萬元。<br />\n<br />\n恒生銀行回覆本報查詢時表明，不評論個別賬戶事宜。警方指相關事宜屬私人事務，與工作無關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CbvUIlad52riHFe0vWNHvZl9jvA=/510x365/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P3QH25FYANCWFOCR2QOEWKSDWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCbvUIlad52riHFe0vWNHvZl9jvA%3D%2F510x365%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP3QH25FYANCWFOCR2QOEWKSDWQ.jpg&h=34bed029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國安處長蔡展鵬上周二還清火炭御龍山單位按揭貸款。"},{"pid":"0511c02bc5f7c39053854ab43f067dd68b08bada","tid":2441360,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8koEs2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8koEs2.gif&h=1e21ebb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c65774512f250f5b78f3154d74ebc6f837dde852","tid":2441360,"uid":76657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚平千幾萬咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正乞衣<br />\n抵你做狗奶我鞋底"},{"pid":"bf5319c6685fcb968b101d28c8cfd93c7144f573","tid":2441360,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"icac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355903272a3436502b5e0fc28eb32d996a1a7a0b","tid":2441360,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"收入與財產不相稱去左邊"},{"pid":"3d6f7e3b4d50b1a018703a0328d48b0812c36c10","tid":2441360,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"原來住御龍山<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d0568f4b17f468f683a5a2b76492845493a8a4","tid":2441360,"uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:37:18.000Z","msg":"80億維穩費就係幫手贖樓用！"},{"pid":"faa468